channel.title: Antagonist of Mine - Azure Onyxscore [DnB, Upbeat]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/azureonyx/antagonist-of-mine/s-ZzdU5VLgnPL
Here's towards my next album, probably releasing in 2023, knowing how long my previous album took to make.
This track is a remix of one of my early Auxy tracks back in 2017ish, around the time where Auxy for iOS was still in it's infancy. You can hear the original mix [here](https://audius.co/azureonyxscore/enemy-of-mine-18607)
